                            <comment id="13679487" author="pierre.bourret" created="Mon, 10 Jun 2013 13:19:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached patch defines getPolicy() and getCreationStrategy() in both ProvidedService and ProvidedServiceDescription classes.&lt;/p&gt;

